{"tid":2512804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本鄉下妹求職誤入AV公司，路人長相竟擊敗同期王牌女優！","createTime":"2021-05-02T04:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T04:30:40.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d45cbb579db4ae7db815551b410c4dd5e4ada5d","tid":2512804,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"日本知名成人視頻網站「FANZA」（舊 DMM.R18）的銷量榜，長期被當紅女優霸占。例如大家熟悉的三上悠亞、高橋聖子等。<br />\n<br />\n但在 2019 年間，曾經短暫出現過一位被稱為「灰姑娘」的傳奇級新人。<br />\n<br />\n她雖然長相平凡，但業績甚至一度勝過了同公司的王牌女優小島南！<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F0e822ac9j00qsgfci002nc000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F0e822ac9j00qsgfci002nc000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=09fcc5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近，日本綜藝節目日就邀請到了這位傳奇 AV 女優「佐藤りこ」（Riko）。<br />\n<br />\n今年 26 歲的她，看上去非常平凡，就連節目主持人都形容：「像個乖乖女，完全沒有 AV 女優的光芒。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F3bef3a1fj00qsgfci001uc000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F3bef3a1fj00qsgfci001uc000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=4b5e9bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然佐藤的外表長得樸素，卻成為了 2019 年成人視頻網站「FANZA」最高銷量女優。<br />\n<br />\n下面這部就是令佐藤爆紅的「企劃系列」視頻，封面連佐藤的名字也沒有。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F00e8da40j00qsgfci0029c000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F00e8da40j00qsgfci0029c000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=65abcbb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可是，這部看似平凡的視頻竟然大受歡迎，光是預告片已經有超過 87 萬人觀看？？？<br />\n<br />\n同公司的王牌女優小島南也不敵佐藤，同期發售的作品播放量只有 5 萬次瀏覽量，遠遠比不上佐藤的 87 萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F0e422026j00qsgfci001sc000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F0e422026j00qsgfci001sc000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=c7c8b584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底佐藤有著什麼樣的魅力，能吸引大批「老司機」付費觀看呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來，佐藤之前只是一個高爾夫球球童，當時她一直有個當藝人的夢想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是，當她在最後關頭與事務所簽約時才知道，自己被忽悠簽了一家專拍 AV 的公司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為對自己的胸圍還挺有自信，本著將錯就錯的心態，佐藤成為了 AV 女優。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主持人問：「你的父母能接受嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F4c92b34fj00qsgfci0023c000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F4c92b34fj00qsgfci0023c000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=c8571fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佐藤表示，當初只跟了姐弟說了真相，而他們的反應都很平淡，默默地說了句加油。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出道初期，拍了幾集作品的佐藤依然紅不起來。<br />\n<br />\n當時適逢高爾夫球的旺季，於是她宣布引退，繼續做著球童的老本行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過了一段時間，佐藤決定轉行，這次她的目標是搞笑藝人。<br />\n<br />\n她想嘗試挑戰試試其他行業，仔細考慮後，搞笑藝人或許就是人生目標，於是就去考了專門培訓搞笑藝人的日本公司。<br />\n<br />\n佐藤出道後，在舞台上表演著自創的段子。結果台下觀眾對她編的無聊段子，完全沒有反應。<br />\n<br />\n就這樣，佐藤的自信心瞬間就被擊沉了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後兜了一大圈，她又重回了 AV 行業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F2ffdcf48j00qsgfci001zc000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F2ffdcf48j00qsgfci001zc000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=b5733d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般來說，當紅的女優，例如波多野結衣、小島南等，會被稱為「單體女優」，有的獨立作品。<br />\n<br />\n而佐藤這種剛入行的新人只能當「企劃女優」，連名字都不配出現在封面上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2Feea6b9bcj00qsgfci001ec000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252Feea6b9bcj00qsgfci001ec000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=c9a0c63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然而佐藤似乎撞了大運，「企劃系列」的視頻竟然神奇地爆紅！<br />\n<br />\n預告片中，佐藤穿著格子襯衫，在鏡頭前閑聊。接著開了一罐啤酒，豪爽地喝了起來，讓人有種走錯片場的錯覺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2Fb917c2fbj00qsgfci0013c000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252Fb917c2fbj00qsgfci0013c000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=9ee1ef0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接著，她還莫名其妙地拿起一個頭套，擺弄著說：「這是一會兒要用到的道具嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這條平平無奇的預告片播出後&hellip;&hellip;網站湧入 85 萬觀眾，大量留言表示：「很想看下去！」、「還未滿足！」<br />\n<br />\n隨後正式作品的銷量，拿下了 2019 年的第一名！<br />\n<br />\n主持人分析，那部作品受歡迎的原因是接地氣，就好像有個真正的素人在家中一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就連女主持人也表示：「因為猜不到後續發展，反而很想看！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佐藤就像一位「灰姑娘」，由樸素女孩搖身一變，成為了年度銷量女王。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0502%2F0451bd16j00qsgfci002bc000u000gsm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0502%252F0451bd16j00qsgfci002bc000u000gsm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=70f941c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佐藤透露，當時最高收入每月可有 200 多萬日元（約人民幣 12 萬）。<br />\n<br />\n不過這點收入，相比「單體女優」還是有很大差距的。"},{"pid":"348f78d30802183e6c5dac0080b1fb09b7767d61","tid":2512804,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"cdfbe1d0bb307713a991d3830321ffaf5bc5b5c9","tid":2512804,"uid":30868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"黎香港做電子雞唔使爆紅都隨時搵得仲多"},{"pid":"34649c16ae3ba2d82838b0bdcd06dc7facd2d65d","tid":2512804,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdfbe1d0bb307713a991d3830321ffaf5bc5b5c9","tid":2512804,"uid":30868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"黎香港做電子雞唔使爆紅都隨時搵得仲多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n日本人見字快啲搵Email<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c154c62bbee1b7a0391c9249ed3ed43a3e9caead","tid":2512804,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"348f78d30802183e6c5dac0080b1fb09b7767d61","tid":2512804,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"留名gif 圖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fee979ea33eb6bfcf2dee5ec51648132ac678b7","tid":2512804,"uid":33903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34649c16ae3ba2d82838b0bdcd06dc7facd2d65d","tid":2512804,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdfbe1d0bb307713a991d3830321ffaf5bc5b5c9","tid":2512804,"uid":30868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"黎香港做電子雞唔使爆紅都隨時搵得仲多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n日本人見字快啲搵Email<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:30:40.000Z","msg":"email賣相賣到買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}